        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Visual improvements to "Reorder Attachments" popup</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Sort order was sometimes incorrect in Grouped By views</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Selecting "Match all messages" in Filter Rules dialog did not disable all search criteria</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>S/MIME-only signed messages sometimes incorrectly displayed signature as invalid</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
